♪ My invincible legend right on this Soul Land ♪

19
00:02:20,340 --> 00:02:23,440
[This animation is based on the novel Soul Land]
[written by Tangjia Sanshao]

20
00:02:23,980 --> 00:02:27,650
[Previous Episode]
Show me what you’ve gained from this impulse.

21
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:30,980
The glory of Tang Clan

22
00:02:30,980 --> 00:02:33,550
will surely reappear on Soul Land.

23
00:02:33,550 --> 00:02:38,510
Soul Honor Tang San, I’m sorry
for suspecting you before.

24
00:02:39,290 --> 00:02:42,860
Xiao Wu, we would be together forever, right?

25
00:02:43,540 --> 00:02:46,230
I don’t want to see anyone be absent for breakfast.

26
00:02:46,230 --> 00:02:48,200
Otherwise, you will be at your own risk.

27
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,300
I’ll give you a mission.

28
00:02:49,300 --> 00:02:51,260
Without hurting them,

29
00:02:51,260 --> 00:02:53,150
defeat six of them one by one.

30
00:02:55,070 --> 00:02:59,950
[Soul Land]
[Episode 32]

31
00:03:12,780 --> 00:03:15,300
Come on!

32
00:03:17,070 --> 00:03:18,360
Come on!

33
00:03:18,940 --> 00:03:19,570
Mu Bai.

34
00:03:19,570 --> 00:03:21,340
If you can break my third soul skill,

35
00:03:21,340 --> 00:03:22,760
you win.

36
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,870
Tang San, beware.

37
00:03:28,590 --> 00:03:30,250
Blue Silver Plant. Intertwine.

38
00:03:36,150 --> 00:03:37,190
What’s going on?

39
00:03:42,490 --> 00:03:44,280
<i>Although Blue Silver Plant became thinner,</i>

40
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:46,600
<i>it’s combined with the character
of Human Faced Demon Spider.</i>

41
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:48,260
<i>The toughness is greatly increased.</i>

42
00:03:48,260 --> 00:03:49,320
Second soul skill.

43
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:50,540
Parasitic.

44
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,710
Blue Silver Plant is going to be cut off.

45
00:03:57,710 --> 00:04:02,080
No. Tang San didn’t expect to win
with Blue Silver Plant alone.

46
00:04:02,670 --> 00:04:05,550
He is using Blue Silver Plant to limit Mu Bai,

47
00:04:05,550 --> 00:04:08,410
so he can get the time
to activate his third soul skill.

48
00:04:08,410 --> 00:04:09,870
The true meaning
of a soul master of Controlling Branch

49
00:04:09,870 --> 00:04:12,810
is to control the opponent
since the beginning of the fight

50
00:04:12,810 --> 00:04:14,590
until the end of it.

51
00:04:14,590 --> 00:04:17,200
<i>Is this Little San’s third soul ring?</i>

52
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:37,320
<i>How can Blue Silver Plant defeat me?</i>

53
00:04:51,660 --> 00:04:54,450
<i>Mu Bai, you’re reckless again.</i>

54
00:05:05,220 --> 00:05:06,580
It’s okay now.

55
00:05:07,850 --> 00:05:11,430
Generally, soul masters of Controlling Branch
are weak at attacking.

56
00:05:11,430 --> 00:05:13,960
But they’re strong in controlling.

57
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:15,230
Below Level 60,

58
00:05:15,230 --> 00:05:20,360
they can defeat an opponent with
10-level differences, if they’re good enough.

59
00:05:21,220 --> 00:05:23,780
This is my third soul skill,
Constraint of Spider Web.

60
00:05:23,780 --> 00:05:24,710
Don’t move.

61
00:05:25,020 --> 00:05:27,700
I’ll reabsorb the venom of the spider web.

62
00:05:33,940 --> 00:05:37,220
Mu Bai, as a soul master of Storm Attack Branch,

63
00:05:37,220 --> 00:05:39,530
Controlling Branch is your enemy.

64
00:05:39,530 --> 00:05:41,910
When facing a soul master of Controlling Branch,

65
00:05:41,910 --> 00:05:45,190
the best way is to not giving him
a chance to control you.

66
00:05:45,190 --> 00:05:46,610
In the situation just now,

67
00:05:46,610 --> 00:05:49,850
you should have kept distance
between you and him.

68
00:05:51,130 --> 00:05:54,180
Every soul master has
his own merits and demerits.

69
00:05:54,180 --> 00:05:56,690
There’s no perfect soul master in this world.

70
00:05:56,690 --> 00:05:59,650
But there’s a perfect team.

71
00:06:04,460 --> 00:06:07,530
The power of a person can’t have
the strongest strength.

72
00:06:07,530 --> 00:06:11,230
But a team with mutual understanding
will be unbeatable.

73
00:06:12,810 --> 00:06:15,880
Right now, the seven of you are a team.

74
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,910
When you face enemies together,

75
00:06:17,910 --> 00:06:19,400
the first thing you should do,

76
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:21,260
is to make up for each others’ demerits,

77
00:06:21,260 --> 00:06:24,150
and to optimise everyone’s merits.

78
00:06:24,150 --> 00:06:26,460
Mu Bai, carry on with your class today.

79
00:06:26,460 --> 00:06:29,800
Next, you’ll fight Oscar and Ma Hong Jun.

80
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,690
Yes, Grandmaster.

81
00:06:36,910 --> 00:06:39,700
Boss Dai, you wouldn’t release
your anger on me, right?

82
00:06:39,700 --> 00:06:41,440
Stop the nonsense. Let’s start.

83
00:06:42,590 --> 00:06:46,120
Don’t be afraid, Fatty. I’ll help you.

84
00:06:46,530 --> 00:06:48,650
The Merging of Phoenix.

85
00:07:03,870 --> 00:07:05,920
Second soul skill, Firing Bathing Phoenix.

86
00:07:10,270 --> 00:07:10,640
You!

87
00:07:18,370 --> 00:07:20,240
White Tiger Protection Barrier.

88
00:07:23,710 --> 00:07:25,330
White Tiger Intense Light Wave.

89
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:35,310
After the battle in Star Dou Forest,

90
00:07:35,310 --> 00:07:37,710
I realize that using Phoenix Firing Line
in Firing Bathing Phoenix

91
00:07:37,710 --> 00:07:39,760
can increase its force.

92
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:46,130
Although it uses up much soul power,
the effect is great.

93
00:07:46,130 --> 00:07:48,160
Are you alright, Boss Dai?

94
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:48,880
Hm.

95
00:08:13,420 --> 00:08:16,240
Boss Dai, I’m not fighting alone.

96
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:26,240
<i>The mushroom sausage of Oscar.</i>

97
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:29,200
<i>Flying at the speed of
Phoenix Tail Crest Serpent for a minute.</i>

98
00:08:37,860 --> 00:08:39,420
<i>You only have one minute.</i>

99
00:08:39,430 --> 00:08:40,360
<i>Get rid of this assistant first.</i>

100
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:42,840
<i>- After one minute, the fight will end.</i>
- Flying Mushroom Sausage.

101
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,280
White Tiger Intense Light Wave.

102
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:49,160
<i>Although White Tiger Intense Light Wave
can attack from distance,</i>

103
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:50,930
<i>the distance is only within 20 meters.</i>

104
00:08:50,930 --> 00:08:52,920
<i>- If it’s extended further,</i>
- Super Recovery Big Sausage.

105
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:55,120
<i>a great amount of soul power
will be used up.</i>

106
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:57,900
<i>So much soul power was used in the previous fight.</i>

107
00:08:57,900 --> 00:08:59,190
<i>I’m afraid now...</i>

108
00:09:01,050 --> 00:09:02,750
<i>Since Little Ao achieved Level 30,</i>

109
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:05,380
<i>he can make Super Recovery
Big Sausage in split second.</i>

110
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:31,200
[Soul Land]

111
00:09:32,350 --> 00:09:35,210
<i>He keeps giving them to Fatty effortlessly.</i>

112
00:09:35,210 --> 00:09:37,120
<i>With the support of sausages,</i>

113
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:40,860
<i>Fatty can obviously endure much longer.</i>

114
00:09:40,860 --> 00:09:41,840
Little San.

115
00:09:42,710 --> 00:09:43,840
Yes, Master?

116
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:46,840
Since you used your
third soul skill to Mu Bai just now,

117
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:49,040
so help him fight an opponent.

118
00:09:49,040 --> 00:09:52,000
Xiao Wu, show me your third soul skill.

119
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,550
Okay, Grandmaster.

120
00:10:01,220 --> 00:10:03,550
Little San, you have to be careful.

121
00:10:08,170 --> 00:10:11,120
Little San, do you have to be so alert?

122
00:10:17,560 --> 00:10:20,680
<i>Oh, no. That’s Xiao Wu’s
second soul skill, Charm.</i>

123
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,990
I’ve succeeded.

124
00:10:25,990 --> 00:10:27,590
<i>I was silly.</i>

125
00:10:27,590 --> 00:10:29,830
<i>If I had activated Purple Demon Eye
since I started,</i>

126
00:10:29,830 --> 00:10:31,810
<i>I wouldn’t be so passive.</i>

127
00:10:31,810 --> 00:10:34,080
<i>That’s the enemy of Charm.</i>

128
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,900
<i>Since we came to Shrek School,</i>

129
00:10:35,900 --> 00:10:37,870
<i>I’ve not practiced with Xiao Wu.</i>

130
00:10:37,870 --> 00:10:39,720
<i>I’m reckless this time.</i>

131
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:45,000
Third soul skill.

132
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,590
Constraint of Spider Web.

133
00:10:56,910 --> 00:10:59,140
<i>Xiao Wu disappeared into thin air.</i>

134
00:11:03,920 --> 00:11:05,560
- First soul skill, Arched Body.
<i>- Xiao Wu’s current Arched Body</i>

135
00:11:05,560 --> 00:11:07,620
<i>must have increased up to 120% now.</i>

136
00:11:07,620 --> 00:11:09,850
<i>It can’t be stood up by soul masters
at the same level.</i>

137
00:11:09,850 --> 00:11:11,340
Little San, you’ve lost.

138
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:14,310
No. Constraint of Spider Web.

139
00:11:25,190 --> 00:11:29,650
Super, Super Recovery Big Sausage.

140
00:11:37,820 --> 00:11:39,810
Okay. You may stop now.

141
00:12:15,750 --> 00:12:17,510
Talk about your feelings.

142
00:12:17,510 --> 00:12:20,440
It wasn’t fair. If my soul power wasn’t depleted,

143
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:22,020
they wouldn’t stand a chance.

144
00:12:23,070 --> 00:12:27,260
Would your enemy come
only when your soul power is at its best?

145
00:12:29,730 --> 00:12:32,240
You knew Oscar can provide mushroom sausages,

146
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:34,980
why did you let Ma Hong Jun eat them?

147
00:12:37,610 --> 00:12:39,600
If you stopped him from the beginning,

148
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:41,680
or tried to save up your soul power,

149
00:12:41,680 --> 00:12:43,940
you would have been the winner.

150
00:12:44,790 --> 00:12:46,480
What a nice feeling.

151
00:12:46,480 --> 00:12:49,150
I didn’t expect myself to defeat Boss Dai.

152
00:12:49,150 --> 00:12:50,970
What a nice feeling I have.

153
00:12:50,970 --> 00:12:53,220
Little Ao, the sausages are effective.

154
00:12:53,220 --> 00:12:57,140
Of course. I’m a Soul Honor after all.

155
00:12:58,650 --> 00:12:59,820
Are you proud of it?

156
00:12:59,820 --> 00:13:02,090
Ma Hong Jun, let me ask you.

157
00:13:02,090 --> 00:13:04,640
When the Flying Mushroom Sausage
of Oscar lost its effect,

158
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:06,790
why did you let him fall?

159
00:13:06,790 --> 00:13:10,010
If Mu Bai still had the power to attack him,

160
00:13:10,010 --> 00:13:11,180
what would you do?

161
00:13:12,530 --> 00:13:15,390
And you. As a soul master of Food Branch,

162
00:13:15,390 --> 00:13:19,360
most importantly, you should save yourself.

163
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:23,940
Even if he didn’t help you,
couldn’t you hold on to him to keep flying?

164
00:13:23,940 --> 00:13:27,020
If Dai Mu Bai was an enemy, you would be dead.

165
00:13:27,020 --> 00:13:28,200
Soul Honor?

166
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:30,780
Even if you’re a soul master
of the highest soul level of Food Branch,

167
00:13:30,780 --> 00:13:33,290
you would be nothing in front of a war soul master.

168
00:13:36,460 --> 00:13:37,610
Little San.

169
00:13:38,780 --> 00:13:39,930
Master.

170
00:13:39,930 --> 00:13:42,470
Talk about your fight with Xiao Wu.

171
00:13:42,470 --> 00:13:45,140
Master, I was wrong. I shouldn’t have been reckless.

172
00:13:45,140 --> 00:13:47,360
I was attacked by Xiao Wu’s second soul skill, Charm,

173
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:49,480
and was in a passive situation.

174
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:52,390
Before I knew what her third soul skill was,

175
00:13:52,390 --> 00:13:53,940
I released the spider web hastily,

176
00:13:53,940 --> 00:13:56,220
which caused myself to be
in a more passive situation.

177
00:13:56,220 --> 00:13:57,790
It’s good that you realize your mistake.

178
00:13:57,790 --> 00:13:59,470
Your mistake is the most serious one.

179
00:13:59,470 --> 00:14:01,050
You need full power
even if you’re fighting a weak enemy.

180
00:14:01,050 --> 00:14:04,210
You even made an unforgivable
mistake at the beginning.

181
00:14:04,210 --> 00:14:07,790
Remember, soul masters of Controlling Branch
have to control themselves,

182
00:14:07,790 --> 00:14:09,270
other than controlling your enemies.

183
00:14:09,270 --> 00:14:10,550
Yes, Master.

184
00:14:11,110 --> 00:14:13,410
Your third soul skill should be Teleport, right?

185
00:14:14,010 --> 00:14:15,740
But it’s limited by distance.

186
00:14:15,740 --> 00:14:17,330
If I guess it right,

187
00:14:17,330 --> 00:14:19,210
that should be the power of Lightning Rabbit.

188
00:14:19,210 --> 00:14:24,060
So your third soul ring is
a thousand-year-old Lightning Rabbit.

189
00:14:24,540 --> 00:14:27,820
Teleport is one of the rarest soul skills.

190
00:14:27,820 --> 00:14:29,940
You’ve surprised me well.

191
00:14:29,940 --> 00:14:32,590
The combination of Teleport and Arched Body

192
00:14:32,590 --> 00:14:34,750
will increase your killing effect greatly.

193
00:14:34,750 --> 00:14:37,220
But why did you assume you would win

194
00:14:37,220 --> 00:14:38,930
when you were choking Little San’s neck?

195
00:14:38,930 --> 00:14:40,340
If you could be more careful,

196
00:14:40,340 --> 00:14:42,320
when you saw Little San use Constraint of Spider Web,

197
00:14:42,320 --> 00:14:44,990
you moved away from his attack
before attacking again,

198
00:14:44,990 --> 00:14:47,990
you would have won,
instead of being controlled again.

199
00:14:47,990 --> 00:14:50,210
Are you the so-called Genius Monsters?

200
00:14:50,210 --> 00:14:52,450
Your performance today has disappointed me.

201
00:14:52,450 --> 00:14:55,030
Everyone made unforgivable mistakes.

202
00:14:55,030 --> 00:14:58,130
All of you must be punished.

203
00:15:12,340 --> 00:15:13,900
Here is the punishment.

204
00:15:13,900 --> 00:15:16,630
There are some rocks at the entrance.

205
00:15:16,630 --> 00:15:20,150
Carry them, run to and back from Suo Tuo City.

206
00:15:20,150 --> 00:15:21,730
No soul power is allowed.

207
00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:29,240
You must do it 10 times by noon.

208
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:32,620
Little San, your mistake is the worst. Do it 12 times.

209
00:15:32,620 --> 00:15:34,020
Got it, Master.

210
00:15:34,020 --> 00:15:36,090
Remember, you’re a team.

211
00:15:36,090 --> 00:15:37,600
If one person doesn’t complete it,

212
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:39,510
everyone isn’t allowed to eat.

213
00:15:43,310 --> 00:15:44,640
Do it now.

214
00:15:57,940 --> 00:15:59,360
Why aren’t you running?

215
00:16:00,210 --> 00:16:01,830
We have to run as well?

216
00:16:01,830 --> 00:16:04,150
Zhu Qing and I didn’t make mistakes.

217
00:16:05,340 --> 00:16:07,930
Let me ask you. Who are they to you?

218
00:16:13,390 --> 00:16:15,580
Schoolmates, partners.

219
00:16:15,580 --> 00:16:18,950
If you want to be partners
that can rely on each other,

220
00:16:18,950 --> 00:16:21,060
should you watch your partners be punished

221
00:16:21,060 --> 00:16:22,470
while you’re resting?

222
00:16:22,470 --> 00:16:23,720
I...

223
00:16:36,110 --> 00:16:38,200
Turns out Grandmaster was prepared.

224
00:16:48,590 --> 00:16:50,820
Master treats us differently.

225
00:16:54,970 --> 00:16:58,460
Mu Bai, Fatty and I have
the biggest rocks in our baskets.

226
00:16:58,460 --> 00:17:02,870
Xiao Wu, Zhu Qing and Little Ao follow,
while Rong Rong has the smallest.

227
00:17:02,870 --> 00:17:05,920
It seems that Grandmaster isn’t unreasonable.

228
00:17:10,440 --> 00:17:12,750
A couple of hundred kilometers,

229
00:17:12,760 --> 00:17:16,680
without using soul power.
Isn’t this punishment too heavy?

230
00:17:17,630 --> 00:17:20,530
They don’t eat a big breakfast for anything.

231
00:17:26,140 --> 00:17:28,210
Without suffering as a team,

232
00:17:28,210 --> 00:17:30,090
how can they become true partners?

233
00:17:35,070 --> 00:17:36,010
Let’s go.

234
00:17:42,710 --> 00:17:47,170
Up to you. But the fund of our school...

235
00:17:48,120 --> 00:17:51,370
An honorable Soul Saint can’t even
get such little amount of money.

236
00:17:51,370 --> 00:17:53,620
I don’t want to count on others.

237
00:17:53,620 --> 00:17:56,460
Or else, with my strength...

238
00:20:06,190 --> 00:20:07,410
[Next Episode]
Master mentioned just now,

239
00:20:07,410 --> 00:20:09,030
we’re a team.

240
00:20:09,030 --> 00:20:11,120
The aim of this punishment

241
00:20:11,120 --> 00:20:13,120
is to train our collectivity.

242
00:20:14,620 --> 00:20:16,690
Why are you treating me like this?

243
00:20:16,690 --> 00:20:19,710
Second Brother, isn’t mine here?

244
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:21,630
You...

245
00:20:21,630 --> 00:20:23,970
Boss, save me.

246
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:28,250
If you defeat the three of us,
I will release this pig.

247
00:20:28,250 --> 00:20:32,020
You’re like a dead dog.
Finally, you’re suffering.

248
00:20:34,600 --> 00:20:35,780
Watch this.

